            "chapterTitle": "Exaltation of Modesty",
            "urn": 1606725,
            "body": "<p>Ibn 'Umar (May Allah be pleased with them) reported: Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) passed by a man of the Ansar who was admonishing his brother regarding shyness. Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) said, \"Leave him alone, for modesty is a part of Iman.\"\n</p>\n<p>\n<b>[Al-Bukhari and Muslim]</b>.</p>",
            "grades": []
